					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">tokumaru wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">I don't know why the tutorials insist on reading the controller like that...</div>
<br />
<br />Because it is one of the early lessons in a simple beginners tutorial.  Reading all the buttons at once needs shifting, variables, and subroutines.  Just a few lessons later those are covered and the controller reading is changed.
<br />
<br />Newbies need simplicity to learn first, being "professional" is overwhelming instead of teaching.</div>

